You may set sliding animation for angular advertisement here.<br /><br />The system will set sliding direction by $stylevar[left] variable, for instance if language of board is 'Left to Right', raw HTML will slide from right of screen to the left.<br /><br />If you set 'Yes (Pause on Mouse Over)' for this option, moreover that apply sliding animation when user move the mouse cursor on angular advertisement container, it will stop and when cursor out from its range, will be continue to sliding.<br /><br />Note that if you set this option to true while you have inserted a <em>&lt;MARQUEE&gt;</em> tag for 'Contents' field, all &lt;MARQUEE&gt; tags will be striped from the text.